#. -- Condition: My Race(s): Greenlander or Shek or Hive Prince
#: 1746-gamedata.base:0
msgid "If you want to survive out there you'll need someone who actually knows how to fight.  7500 cats and I'm yours."
msgstr "如果你想在那裡生存，你需要一個真正知道如何戰鬥的人。 7500隻貓，我是你的。"

#. Id: 1746-gamedata.base
#. -- Index: 0.1
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: hire me 5000
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: WEAKER_THAN_ME=1, Tag: -1
#. -- Condition: Who: ME, Condition: PERSONALITY_TAG=1, Tag: TRAITOROUS
#. -- Condition: My Race(s): Greenlander or Shek or Hive Prince
#: 1746-gamedata.base:1
msgid "A rookie like you won't last 5 minutes out in the /SANDS/. Want my help? I charge 7500 Cats"
msgstr ""

#. Id: 1746-gamedata.base
#. -- Index: 0.2
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: hire me 5000
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: WEAKER_THAN_ME=1, Tag: -1
#. -- Condition: Who: ME, Condition: PERSONALITY_TAG=1, Tag: TRAITOROUS
#. -- Condition: My Race(s): Greenlander or Shek or Hive Prince
#: 1746-gamedata.base:2
msgid "I know a rookie when I see one. 7500 Cats, /OUTLANDER/, and I'll watch your back for you."
msgstr ""

#. Id: 1746-gamedata.base
#. -- Index: 0.3
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: hire me 5000
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: WEAKER_THAN_ME=1, Tag: -1
#. -- Condition: Who: ME, Condition: PERSONALITY_TAG=1, Tag: TRAITOROUS
#. -- Condition: My Race(s): Greenlander or Shek or Hive Prince
#: 1746-gamedata.base:3
msgid "You look like you could use some protection, /OUTLANDER/. I can watch your back for you, but it will set you back 7500 Cats. You want a good sword, you gotta pay good Cats for it."
msgstr ""

#. Id: 1747-gamedata.base
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (1746-gamedata.base)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: hire me 5000
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: PLAYERMONEY>7500, Tag: -1
#. Id: 52549-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
